(Sundiata Post) â€“ The Minister of Budget and National Planning, Senator Udoma Udo Udoma, has confirmed the death of his immediate elder brother, Mr Inam Udo Udoma. The sad development happened last Tuesday morning, March 13, 2018, after a brief illness. Special Adviser (Media) to the Minister, Akpandem James announced in a statement on Sunday. He was 66 years old. The late Inam Udoma was a University of Ibadan trained geologist and businessman. He had several business interests and served on a number of boards, including that of Linkage Assurance Plc. He was married with three children and a grandchild.